OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FThousands of people have been affected
OL,8,Fby travel disruption because of the
OL,9,FIran war, reports ITV News' Consumer
OL,10,FEditor Chris Choi
OL,12,FWords by ITV News' Consumer Editor
OL,13,FChris Choi and Senior Consumer
OL,14,FProducer Rachael Allison
OL,16,FExperts say flight cancellations due
OL,17,Fto the war in Iran are at "crisis
OL,18,Flevels".
OL,26,@yD@[OUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FNew figures given to ITV News show
OL,8,Fnearly 80% of flights to and from the
OL,9,FMiddle East have been affected (79.8%).
OL,11,FData from AirHelp, a passenger rights
OL,12,Forganisation, shows over half a
OL,13,Fmillion (506,000) passengers are
OL,14,Faffected.
OL,16,FYet less than 1% are entitled to
OL,17,Fcompensation, because conflict is
OL,18,Fdeemed "extraordinary circumstances",
OL,19,Fexcluding airlines from the usual
OL,20,Fobligations.
OL,26,@zD@HOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
