OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FITV News has been contacted by airline
OL,8,Fcustomers caught in what has become
OL,9,Fthe biggest disruption to aviation
OL,10,Fsince the pandemic.
OL,12,FSamantha and Paul Bartlett went to
OL,13,FThailand to celebrate a birthday, but
OL,14,Ftheir trip started two days before the
OL,15,Fwar in Iran.
OL,17,FTheir airline, which is based in Asia,
OL,18,Fcancelled the return flight, so they
OL,19,Faccepted a refund. But when booking a
OL,20,Freplacement flight, they got a price
OL,21,Fshock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FPaul said: "We were searching other
OL,8,Foptions through the night and it
OL,9,Fbecame apparent quite quickly that it
OL,10,Fwasn't going to be an easy way to get
OL,11,Fback home.
OL,13,F"I tried to book about 20 flights and
OL,14,Fat the point of paying for that
OL,15,Fflight, it would time out and tell me
OL,16,Fthe flight is gone," he added.
OL,18,F"Some of them were double in price
OL,19,Fonce you got to the checkout".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FThe couple told us that some of the
OL,8,Fflights were around #7,000, but they
OL,9,Fsaw other flights from Thailand to the
OL,10,FUK around #11,000-#12,000.
OL,12,FThe pair managed to book a flight
OL,13,Fcosting them just over #3,500.
OL,15,FIndiGo Airline did not respond to ITV
OL,16,FNews' response for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
