OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FConsumer tip: Flying to the UK with
OL,8,Fairlines not based here or in the EU
OL,9,Fmeans you don't get standardised
OL,10,Frights. It's down to the company's own
OL,11,Fpolicies. In this case, refund of
OL,12,Foriginal fare - and no more.
OL,14,FKatherine Malcolm was away with her
OL,15,Fhusband and 2 children in New Zealand.
OL,16,FTheir return flight via Dubai was
OL,17,Fcancelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FKatherine said: "The options were to
OL,8,Frebook, which at first we were like,
OL,9,Fyeah I've got upcoming surgery we need
OL,10,Fto get home as soon as possible, we've
OL,11,Fgot work, the kids have got school, so
OL,12,Fwe said book us on the next flight
OL,13,Fout".
OL,15,FUnfortunately, Katherine had found
OL,16,Fthat the flights soon sold out and the
OL,17,Fnext best flight was at the end of
OL,18,FMarch.
OL,20,FFor the family, this was not an
OL,21,Foption, so she chose a refund instead.
OL,26,@oD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
