OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FKatherine said: "Then I waited six
OL,8,Fdays, no email, no sign of a refund."
OL,10,FConsumer tip: We contacted Katharine's
OL,11,Fonline travel agent, Expedia, who told
OL,12,Fus "an agent error" caused the refund
OL,13,Fdelay and they added a #700 "gesture
OL,14,Fof goodwill due to the inconvenience"
OL,16,FClare Ding booked a package holiday to
OL,17,FDubai.
OL,19,FShe told us "We booked this holiday
OL,20,Fway before Christmas, never ever been
OL,21,Fthere. We were so excited.
OL,26,@tD@DOUtD@SO]uD@]OUvD@eO]{D@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,F"It (the war) just kept escalating,
OL,8,Fobviously very clear that we couldn't
OL,9,Fdo this holiday anymore.
OL,11,F"And that's when the frustrations
OL,12,Freally started. We could not get hold
OL,13,Fof the holiday company, sadly we
OL,14,Fcouldn't speak to a human being.
OL,16,F"I think I wanted some reassurance
OL,17,Fmore than anything, that this was
OL,18,Fgoing to be sorted out and we would
OL,19,Fget a full refund".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
