PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774490589
OL,3,CFlight cancellations at 'crisis
OL,4,Clevels' amid Iran war as thousands
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FConsumer tip: If there's been a lack
OL,8,Fof communication from the airline or
OL,9,Fthe online travel agent, passengers
OL,10,Fare entitled to a refund or a
OL,11,Frebooking. The travel agent,
OL,12,FLastminute.com told us they are
OL,13,F"strictly following official
OL,14,Frecommendations, regulations and our
OL,15,Fsuppliers policies" and are currently
OL,16,F"managing a huge volume of customers"
OL,18,FThe aviation sector says it's doing
OL,19,Fall it can to minimise the impact on
OL,20,Fpassengers but is facing huge pressure.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@SO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
